Detailed Description

This packet is a reply to the update traffic cost request packet.

Does not contain anything except for the status (in ReplyPacket).

A RouteModule sending this packet to TM-leader will set status OK if everything went ok, NOTFOUND if one or more nodes were not found in the map and MAPNOTFOUND if the map was not found in the RouteModule at all.
